reviewText: Scooby Doo is always excellent and it's cheaper buying this pack then the 3 movies(SD and the Goblin King, SD and the Alien Invaders, and SD Abracabra Doo)separately. None of the discs were broken or scratched either.
It was good expect one of the discs was damaged in travel but my daughter love other two. The aliens invaders is the one thats crack and won't play.
My grandchildren love scooby doo and this will give them hours of watching while we are riding.
7 yr. old granddaughter so far has never watched anything Scooby she didn't like. These 3 movies are no exception. Scooby is always a winner here!
would be interested in seeing additional fun packs with various scooby movies to include camp scare and other less known titles
It's Scooby Doo, can never go wrong entertaining with Scooby!

My kids love these. The Alien Invaders one has different animation and only Fred's voice is the same, so those that prefer the standard style it takes getting used to. Worth it to get the other two, though. Especially Abracadabra Doo.
Five year old grandson loves Scooby-Doo.  These are longer movies rather than episodes.
My son loved this collection of Scooby Doo movies.  The price was great as well.
